Description: Native PlantUML diagram viewer and editor
 gPlantUML is a native GTK4/libadwaita application for viewing and editing
 PlantUML diagrams. It provides real-time preview of your diagrams as you
 type, with full syntax highlighting and error detection.
 .
 Features:
  * Native rendering using Graphviz (no Java required)
  * Real-time diagram preview
  * Syntax highlighting for PlantUML
  * Support for Sequence, Class, Activity, State, Use Case, Component diagrams
  * Export to SVG, PNG, and PDF
  * Dark mode support
